  "body": "### Overview\r\nIt should be possible to wait for _all_ pending transactions with a single call.\r\n\r\n### Specification\r\nGiven the pending tx objects are kept within `history`, it makes sense to me to include this as a method on the `TxHistory` object.\r\n\r\n```python\r\ndef TxHistory.wait_pending(n_confs: int = 1) -> None:\r\n    ...\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt may also make sense to include an API similar to `history.filter` so you can wait for e.g. only transactions from a specific sender.\r\n",
